{
  "stem": "25381.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my sister and a cousin of mine-- my middle sister and a cousin of mine-- they were already on the train to run because the Russians said to us Jewish people, run away!",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Run away!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't stay here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You come with us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You come with us to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're killing the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they came already from deep from Poland and they saw what they're doing to the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my sister was already on the train to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then in the middle of this, she turned around and she thought to herself, no, I'm going to leave my mother alone, and my sisters, and I should survive?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they returned back and she came back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they killed her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She's not alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but when they-- when the German came-- so we were still [INAUDIBLE] in the house-- in-- the people, the Jewish people, in their homes, living in their own homes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from the beginning, they organized.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took Jewish people like it was-- like a mayor, for instance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave, right away, a notice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Today you have to bring so much and so much silver to them, to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So whatever, the Jewish-- if not, we're going to come at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're going to kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the beginning, in 1941, when they occupied the territory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the second day, you have to bring all the gold that you have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then you have to bring all the furs that you have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So every-- and they organized, like, about five, six healthy, strong, Jewish men, you know, educated and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were like the leaders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they went to the Jewish homes and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to come in this and this house.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
